      <a href="/brands/apple" style="color: #011a3a; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">View Guides &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
      <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Samsung Repair Guides</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive tutorials for the Galaxy S and A series.</p>
      <a href="/brands/samsung" style="color: #011a3a; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">View Guides &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
      <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Xiaomi/Redmi Guides</h3>
      <p>Easy-to-follow teardowns and screen replacements.</p>
      <a href="/brands/xiaomi" style="color: #011a3a; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">View Guides &rarr;</a>
